Overview

This dashboard shows Malware overview related to the Cybereason Integration.

The dashboard is made to provide general statistics and show the ingested malware logs from Cybereason.

It shows the breakdown of malware by needs attention, type, element type and status. It presents the distribution of malware events across timestamp. The dashboard also includes the top 10 malware by detection engine. In addition, it illustrates the malware and data model details.
